{"tid":654440,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"搵一隻關於 巨型蟻入侵地球 嘅RPG劇情FLASH GAME","createTime":"2018-05-05T15:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T04:36:04.000Z","uid":155710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d853d221ab4c45f97a88210112c1704f0b376cd4","tid":654440,"uid":155710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"以前小學雞年代(03年左右)<br />\n有一隻英文FLASH GAME, 話個世界比巨型蟻入侵,<br />\n地圖上好多處都有蟻洞, D蟻會喺果度出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD蟻既level由佢腹部既顏色睇得出, 最廢既冇色, 然後勁d有粒白色點, 勁D有黃色,紅色,綠色...<br />\n<br />\n主角就周圍搵有咩方法解決, 避開D蟻/殺死D蟻去一個目的地引發劇情<br />\n有得拎槍/中後期仲有得揸住架坦克<br />\n<br />\nENDING係拎住架坦克入蟻巢見到隻超巨型蟻后,<br />\n最後炸左個巢, 揸住架坦克逃出生天。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打記得隻GAME叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡"},{"pid":"9edefb1df3a106b53d2d0037e93fbeb99423a930","tid":654440,"uid":155710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba2e523564f545bb4734433f4c9f56cd05ca189","tid":654440,"uid":35926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"edf"},{"pid":"c7f01659217c5d6d402a9fcb694b92b97dee0977","tid":654440,"uid":155710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba2e523564f545bb4734433f4c9f56cd05ca189","tid":654440,"uid":35926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"edf"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:25:48.000Z","msg":"Tks ching但唔係。我果隻係好耐既2d flash game黎"},{"pid":"e42b787b33d0909f1a711047ff24fae9f0e28b6d","tid":654440,"uid":22599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52faf82df8361ca293307e5a122dc9b42eab1957","tid":654440,"uid":155710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e42b787b33d0909f1a711047ff24fae9f0e28b6d","tid":654440,"uid":22599,"like":0,"dislike":